{"tid":299309,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[1+1=2] 愛炫美夥銀行推「順逆按揭」吸客","createTime":"2017-06-27T03:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T11:26:44.000Z","uid":8441,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ace1736ae2f3a6fbb7bd8cf1cb6dd0fba4160e4c","tid":299309,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T03:29:34.000Z","msg":"發展商為求吸客無所不用其極，近年「靠父幹」一族冒起，長實（01113）荃灣海之戀．愛炫美（下稱愛炫美）計劃夥拍銀行，推出「順逆按揭」一條龍計劃，以逆安揭協助靠父幹一族，減輕子女供樓負擔。<br />\n<br />\n長實地產投資董事郭子威表示，集團正與7家銀行商議，推行順逆按揭一條龍計劃，買家可向發展商承接85%高成數按揭外，亦針對年齡超過55歲的父母，擁有樓齡50年以下已斷供的物業，提供流動資金，變相將已斷供物業套現，令父母可於不影響生活質素的情況下為子女支付首期，當中不涉及發展商補貼。<br />\n<br />\n長實高級營業經理封海倫表示，愛炫美料日內上載樓書，本周內開價，示範單位亦有機會周內開放供參觀。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/article/id/1593992/%E6%84%9B%E7%82%AB%E7%BE%8E%E5%A4%A5%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%8E%A8%E3%80%8C%E9%A0%86%E9%80%86%E6%8C%89%E6%8F%AD%E3%80%8D%E5%90%B8%E5%AE%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkej.com%2Fdailynews%2Farticle%2Fid%2F1593992%2F%25E6%2584%259B%25E7%2582%25AB%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25A4%25A5%25E9%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%258E%25A8%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%25A0%2586%25E9%2580%2586%25E6%258C%2589%25E6%258F%25AD%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%2590%25B8%25E5%25AE%25A2&d=%2BU4DPnDw0U%2F5gYyF12vnWaS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=617740b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/article/id/1593992/%E6%84%9B%E7%82%AB%E7%BE%8E%E5%A4%A5%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%8E%A8%E3%80%8C%E9%A0%86%E9%80%86%E6%8C%89%E6%8F%AD%E3%80%8D%E5%90%B8%E5%AE%A2</a>"},{"pid":"1fd8426aab4f503fd4be3a3f5032b96959ed154b","tid":299309,"uid":64576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T08:29:12.000Z","msg":"100%按揭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d2e578032d64a39e219113277e67878a646e07","tid":299309,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T08:33:08.000Z","msg":"直接按撚左層樓再買唔得咩咁"},{"pid":"ca4d69431a5869ea5dbdec62b0646cecbb53fb83","tid":299309,"uid"